title: Social Studies Practice Test 3
intro_text:
Social Studies

Welcome to the Social Studies Practice Test!

This test is 25 questions, which is half the length of an official GED Test. You will not be timed.

The goal is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the GED Test.

If you are unsure of an answer, click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later.
